* Gaining Access
 
 To apply for a BIRN cluster SSH account an email shall be sent to {{{mailto:support@nbirn.net}support@nbirn.net}} 
 containing the following items:
 
 * Subject: "SSH access request for birn-cluster0".
 
 * SSH public key attached (created with an 8 characters or greater passphrase).
 
 * Contact information (email and phone).
